Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.86,0:00:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inherited will...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.53,0:00:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The tide of the times... People's dreams...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.41,0:00:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}These things cannot be stopped.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.20,0:00:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as people seek the answer of freedom,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.29,0:00:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}these things will never cease to be!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.64,0:00:42.02,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,mirai dake shinjiteru dareka ga warattemo kamawanai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:47.52,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,hashitteru jounetsu ga anata o kiramekaseru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.52,0:00:53.53,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,mabushi sugi, demo mitsumete itai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.53,0:00:57.03,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,dokka "bigaku" kanjiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.33,0:01:03.71,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,dare ni mo nitenai yume no senaka o
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:06.98,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,oikakete oikaketeku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.98,0:01:10.27,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,doramatikku te ni ireru made
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.18,0:01:22.33,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,dare ni mo mienai yume no katachi o
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.33,0:01:25.39,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,tsukamaete tsukamaeteku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.39,0:01:31.40,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,watashi wa tsuite yuku kara atsui kimochi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.40,0:01:34.49,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,tsujitsuma awase betsu ni iranai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:37.84,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,arifureta nichijou yori mo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:41.08,OP2-Romaji,,0,0,0,,paradaisu mezashite hashire
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.64,0:00:42.02,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,{\q2}I only believe in the future, I don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:47.52,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,that racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.52,0:00:53.53,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,it's too bright, but I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.53,0:00:57.03,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.33,0:01:03.71,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,I follow, follow in the footsteps of a dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:06.98,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.98,0:01:10.27,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.18,0:01:22.33,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.33,0:01:25.39,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,of a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.39,0:01:31.40,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go with you, so passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.40,0:01:34.49,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,I don't really need everything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:37.84,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:41.08,OP2-English,,0,0,0,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 10,0:01:56.67,0:02:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing, old guy?! \NMove this rock!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.97,0:02:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect timing!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:02.64,0:02:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing here, anyway?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.22,0:02:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the deal, Nami?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.93,0:02:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Dinosaur!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.73,0:02:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There's someone on this island!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.78,0:02:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:28.83,0:02:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.25,0:02:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,10,000 Kilogram Press!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.13,0:02:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. 3. Please excuse the codename. \NI'm a mere formative artist.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.26,0:02:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is my realist painter assistant, \NMiss Golden Week.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.64,0:02:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. 3?! The Wax-Wax Fruit man?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.06,0:02:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a "candle man" who controls \Nthe wax he secretes from his body.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.49,0:03:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are gonna pay for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.25,0:03:23.22,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,2000)\pos(264,115)}The Devilish Candle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.25,0:03:23.22,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,2000)\pos(396,460)}Tears of Regret and \NTears of Anger
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.78,0:03:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.24,0:03:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.87,0:03:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This{\i0} is why I can't stand unsophisticated dolts.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.37,0:03:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm creating a work of art, obviously.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.00,0:04:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be a good little girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.13,0:04:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you honestly think {\i1}you{\i0} could escape from Baroque Works?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.85,0:04:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially when someone with a \Nthirty-million-berry bounty winds up like that?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.07,0:04:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy I could thank them for what happened at Whisky Peak.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.44,0:04:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You wannabe pirates should \Nnever have stuck your noses
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.28,0:04:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,into such delicate issues as this.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.16,0:04:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We've already captured your \Nswordsman friend and the other girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.25,0:04:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You caught Zoro?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.79,0:04:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you guys're gonna get cut down!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.63,0:04:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.75,0:04:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You still talk big,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.84,0:04:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,even after one of my Kicky Bombs to the face?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.80,0:04:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't hurt me with that!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.09,0:04:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna kick you guys' asses!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.73,0:04:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.28,0:05:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.70,0:05:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.88,0:05:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,– Fool! \N– Luffy-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.64,0:05:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-{\i1}san{\i0}! Luffy-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.85,0:05:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Miss Valentine.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.56,0:05:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.60,0:05:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp-{\i1}san{\i0}! Karoo!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.75,0:05:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.37,0:06:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it up! Give it up!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.75,0:06:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Once solidified, my Candle Jacket is as hard as iron!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.05,0:06:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You Giants may have brutish strength,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.43,0:06:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,but it becomes all but useless \Nonce you've been caught.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.60,0:06:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Using your brain is the key.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.85,0:06:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to uselessly face you head-on.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.69,0:06:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You lowered your guard \Nas you reveled in victory,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.61,0:06:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Red Ogre Broggy.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.86,0:06:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't glare at me like that. \NYou're terrifying me so!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.91,0:06:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be happy! \NYour long, long battle has come to an end!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.92,0:06:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You fought for a whole century \Nfor your so-called pride, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.42,0:06:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't the taste of victory \Nbe especially sweet, then?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.13,0:06:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it {\i1}is{\i0} the fruit of others' assistance...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.01,0:06:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.55,0:06:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you! You don't mean to say...!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.64,0:07:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But the final victory belongs to me!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.36,0:07:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you aware that the large bounties on your heads from long ago
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.74,0:07:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,come to 200 million berries total?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.49,0:07:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Even today this holds true!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.33,0:07:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.37,0:07:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel as if I've discovered a long-lost treasure!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.50,0:07:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So {\i1}that's{\i0} what you're after, huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.13,0:07:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. 3!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.59,0:07:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We brought her.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.42,0:07:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Our company's little traitor.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.34,0:07:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What took so long? \NI was getting sick of waiting.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.05,0:07:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Your methods are too underhanded, Mr. 3!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.60,0:07:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Planting bombs in Dorry-{\i1}san{\i0}'s alcohol...!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.43,0:07:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.23,0:07:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Alcohol?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.02,0:07:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The alcohol {\i1}I{\i0} gave him?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.40,0:07:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Dorry! How was your drink?! \NHit the spot, didn't it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.32,0:07:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... It tasted "godly"...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.16,0:07:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's what you meant, Dorry?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.33,0:08:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wretched little girl, giving our tricks away.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.17,0:08:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, no matter. \NThere's nothing you can do now, anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.80,0:08:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Candle...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.63,0:08:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...Lock!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.02,0:08:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. 5!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.60,0:08:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring the swordsman and the girl!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.94,0:08:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We're about to begin!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.82,0:08:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Extra Big Candle Set!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.45,0:09:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,T-This is Mr. 3's ability?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.79,0:09:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.00,0:09:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Here they are.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.96,0:09:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How naive.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.97,0:09:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Being ridiculed by people of \Ntheir caliber is so embarrassing
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.97,0:09:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'm pissed at myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.64,0:09:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't help that you're weak.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.27,0:09:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What was that?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.98,0:09:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing! \NJust set the candles up quickly!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.27,0:09:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Set?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.69,0:09:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.69,0:09:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}... Mr. Bushido...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.40,0:10:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Vivi! What happened?! \NWeren't you with Luffy?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.28,0:10:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I was, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.87,0:10:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're wondering about Straw Hat, \NI took care of him myself!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.41,0:10:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an easy job, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.29,0:10:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You did?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.28,0:10:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, friends, to my service set!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.89,0:11:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this how it feels to be \Na candle stuck in a cake?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.56,0:11:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that spinning thing up there?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.19,0:11:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And I can't move my legs...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.28,0:11:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course they're not gonna let us move.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.36,0:11:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the enemy.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.24,0:11:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn. It's hard.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.87,0:11:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus I can't put any strength \Ninto it from this stance.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.92,0:11:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's raining down!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.42,0:11:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,May you enjoy my "Candle Service"!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.05,0:11:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The wax haze falling from above you
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.76,0:11:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,will eventually change you into wax figures!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.22,0:11:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll become perfect "human models"
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.56,0:11:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,that not even I could achieve with my skills!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.02,0:11:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wax figures will have \Nliterally captured your spirit!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.36,0:12:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Now die, in the name of art.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.07,0:12:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw that!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.70,0:12:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do {\i1}we{\i0} have to turn into {\i1}your{\i0} works of art?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.91,0:12:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Broggy-{\i1}san{\i0}! \NQuit sitting there and go on a rampage!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.75,0:12:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna get turned into \Na wax figure too, you know!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.46,0:12:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, talk about a huge person...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.13,0:12:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything you say to him is pointless!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.47,0:12:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He just now realized he foolishly \Nshed proud, joyful tears of victory
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.31,0:12:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,after killing his friend Dorry, \Nwith whom he fought for 100 years,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.81,0:12:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,but without even noticing that he \Nhad suffered injuries beforehand!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.73,0:12:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Or did you perhaps cry for your friend, instead?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.91,0:12:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever the case, there's no \Nundoing what you've done now, fool!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.92,0:13:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.84,0:13:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.97,0:13:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,From the moment we first exchanged blows...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.77,0:13:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...I knew Dorry was hiding something.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.35,0:13:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.86,0:13:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You lie!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.23,0:13:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, then why didn't you cease your fighting?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.03,0:13:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't see a shred of pity in the way you heartily cut him down!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.33,0:13:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A pipsqueak who doesn't even \Nknow the first thing about duels
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.04,0:13:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,would never understand \Nthe meaning of those tears!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.92,0:13:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you know?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.55,0:13:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying I should shame a warrior
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.01,0:13:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,who hides the fact he's been \Nweakened and tries to fight anyway?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.01,0:13:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A warrior who'll go that far to \Nkeep fighting doesn't deserve pity!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.52,0:14:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And now... I know the reason behind it.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.57,0:14:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I know, I'm going to finish things with my own two hands!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.95,0:14:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the very least I can \Ndo for my dear friend Dorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.92,0:14:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Broggy-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.40,0:14:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,– Broggy-{\i1}san{\i0}! \N– Broggy-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.73,0:14:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What an annoying, talkative monster.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.45,0:14:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Usopp...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.95,0:14:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.66,0:14:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you let them get away with this?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.33,0:15:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No... I can't...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.89,0:15:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you... not stand this?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.15,0:15:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! \NLet's all three of us go beat them senseless!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.03,0:15:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Broggy-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.15,0:15:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How dumb!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.24,0:15:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I underestimated how brutishly \Nstrong these Giants can be!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.16,0:15:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It would seem you need to be seized completely!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.88,0:15:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wax-Wax Arts! Handcuffs!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.01,0:15:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just getting started!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.01,0:15:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And now for the finishing touch!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.68,0:16:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.15,0:16:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't move now, can you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.54,0:16:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How can he be so horrific?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.67,0:16:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, then! Accelerate, Candle Service!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.17,0:16:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn these people into wax figures!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.64,0:16:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,M-My chest is starting to hurt...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.43,0:16:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The wax haze is getting into our lungs!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.77,0:16:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, we're going to turn \Ninto wax figures from the inside out!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.23,0:16:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Yes! Make it look like you're in as much pain as you can!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.57,0:16:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Expressions of pain and agony \Nare the very things I seek in art!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.95,0:16:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,May you solidify while filled with terror!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.41,0:17:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You call this art, you creepy topknot freak?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.08,0:17:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you do that to Broggy-{\i1}san{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.08,0:17:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys {\i1}are{\i0} going to regret this! \NYou got that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.26,0:17:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Scream and holler all you want!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.26,0:17:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For 100 years...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.11,0:17:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...day in and day out, we fought and fought...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.78,0:17:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...and dueled only because of our \Npride of Elbaf, village of warriors!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.70,0:17:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yet... why are we being subjected \Nto this, Elbaf, god of war?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.79,0:17:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If this is how we're to meet our end, Elbaf...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.92,0:17:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...don't you think it's unfair?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.13,0:18:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why won't you let us die in battle?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.72,0:18:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What a look!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.93,0:18:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! That sorrow! \NThat grief! That struggle!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.31,0:18:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What a marvelous work of art!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.82,0:18:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Elbaf!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.82,0:18:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! My hands won't move!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.86,0:18:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna die this way! \NCan't we do something?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.37,0:18:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,My body's already turning stiff!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.45,0:18:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.08,0:18:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro! Do something!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.54,0:18:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, old man.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.58,0:18:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You can still move, can't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.88,0:18:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So can I.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.09,0:18:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Whadya say we crush these guys together?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.76,0:18:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Zoro! What are you doing?! \NYou're not seriously gonna...!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.56,0:18:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.35,0:18:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna cut your own legs?! \NQuit joking around!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.77,0:18:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no joke. \NIt's the only way out of here.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.07,0:18:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you two gonna do?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.07,0:18:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?! \NIt's pointless!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.61,0:18:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you do get down from here \Nthat way, they'll catch you again!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.32,0:19:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way to know that unless we try!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.99,0:19:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna kick the bucket \Nif we stay here anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.99,0:19:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's put up some ugly struggling!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.04,0:19:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no reason to die heroically \Nfor these pieces of scum!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.46,0:19:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.71,0:19:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell? Is he crazy?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.42,0:19:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He's bluffing! \NThere's no way he could do that!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.13,0:19:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He's merely acting tough!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.89,0:19:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What a cheeky runt.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.43,0:19:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pathetic. \NIt seems I had even lost the will to fight.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.11,0:19:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll fight alongside you and your fighting spirit!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.11,0:19:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be serious, right?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.32,0:19:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How will you be able to fight afterward?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.53,0:19:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.08,0:19:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I plan to win.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.54,0:19:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who are these guys?! \NThey're off their rocker!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.42,0:19:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What kind of man is he?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.13,0:20:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I've seen this look somewhere before...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.17,0:20:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Vivi!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.05,0:20:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you prepared not to die?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.01,0:20:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait! I'll fight, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.56,0:20:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,– Vivi! \N– Alright, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.98,0:20:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it, runt!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.35,0:20:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid! \NWhat can you possibly do?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.49,0:20:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.74,0:20:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna kick your asses, just so you know!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.08,0:20:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.08,0:20:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,– Let's do it, Usopp! \N– Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.75,0:20:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Bird!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.55,0:20:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy! Usopp!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.42,0:20:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Karoo!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.55,0:20:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Broggy! \NWe've taken on your frustration!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.76,0:20:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.72,0:20:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Beat those guys up so much \Nthey lose their original forms
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.31,0:20:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and send them flying far off somewhere!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.81,0:20:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I will!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.69,0:20:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,These guys spoiled the old giant guys' duel!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.69,0:21:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're the one with the \Nhighest bounty in the East Blue?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.57,0:21:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My, how Navy Headquarters' standards have fallen!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.36,0:21:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,– Whoa! What a weird head! \N– Quiet, you!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.91,0:21:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,– It's the number 3, and it's on fire! \N– Shut up!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.37,0:21:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Break this pillar first, Luffy!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.25,0:21:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We're about to turn into wax figures!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.00,0:21:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? You're in trouble?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.25,0:21:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, there was no problem at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.63,0:21:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Your leg!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.09,0:21:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. \NI went about halfway through, I'd say.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.09,0:21:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,How is that no problem at all?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.22,0:21:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, could you bust this pillar for us, Luffy?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.73,0:21:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I leave the rest to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.94,0:21:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, no problem!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.44,0:21:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be so sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:40.73,0:21:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Dunno what it is, but let's break that thing!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.03,0:21:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.45,0:21:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a bit of a different person today!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.08,0:21:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry it up! We're gonna solidify!
